high_descs: pick up the potato on the table
turn around and head to the microwave
place the potato to cook and take it out
place the potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cooked potato in the sink

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the island on the right.
Pick up the potato from the center of the island.
Hold the potato and turn around to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the potato inside. Turn on the microwave and then open the door and take out the potato.
Carry the potato and turn left, then left again and face the sink on the right.
Place the potato inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat and place a potato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to the kitchen island.
Pick up the round potato off of the island.
Turn around to face the microwave
Place the potato into the microwave to cook.
Remove the potato and walk to the sink across the room
Place the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato in the microwave and put it in the sink to cool
